# Admin Frontend — Linksy

## Scope
- System Admin console at `/admin` — JWT role `Admin` in `user.roles`
- Group chat admin (`memberRole: admin`) is separate — do not reuse for system admin

## PRD (source of truth)
- Master PRD: **backend repo** `docs/admin-prd.md`
- Stub in this repo: `docs/admin-prd.md` (links to backend)
- When implementing, `@` backend PRD via multi-root workspace or paste AC from section 6–7

## Allowed paths (MVP)
- `src/app/(admin)/` — layout, pages, guard
- `src/lib/api/admin.ts` — Admin API client
- `src/lib/types/user.ts` — add `roles?: string[]`
- `src/lib/hooks/` — admin hooks if needed

## Do not (MVP)
- Embed admin UI in `SocialWorkspace` or chat components
- Add SignalR for admin CRUD
- Change backend C# files (frontend repo only)

## Patterns to follow
- Axios: `src/lib/api/axios.ts` + `withCredentials`
- API modules: copy style from `src/lib/api/auth.ts`
- Auth guard: mirror `(main)/layout.tsx` + check `roles.includes("Admin")`
- UI: existing shadcn components in `src/components/ui/`

## Tickets (this repo)
- M3: types + `admin.ts` client
- M4: `(admin)` layout + redirect non-admins to `/dashboard`
- M5: users list, detail, create, toggle, reset password

## Security (UI)
- Hide admin nav unless system Admin
- Confirm dialogs for reset password / delete
- Prefer deactivate over delete in UI
